  "text": [
    "Chewing slowly,",
    "Only after I\u2019d eaten",
    "My grandmother,",
    "Mother,",
    "Son-in-law,",
    "Two brothers-in-law,",
    "And father-in-law",
    "(His big family included)",
    "In that order,",
    "And had for dessert",
    "The town\u2019s inhabitants,",
    "Did I find, says Kabir,",
    "The beloved that I\u2019ve become",
    "One with."
  ],
  "title": "Chewing slowly",
  "year": ""
